- Reference set for calibration drift detection
- Automated canary performance evaluation

**2. code/experiment_analysis.py**
- Score divergence analysis (correlation between evaluators)
- Keyword stuffing detection with density metrics
- Temporal drift analysis (tracks score changes over iterations)
- Automated report generation

**Usage after experiment:**

